Name: Subscribe & Punch!
About the game: This is a demo version of Subscribe & Punch, including 2 characters. Subscribe & Punch! is an easy to play versus fighting game based on the wacky YouTubers universe. Roast the face of your opponents and experiment various humorous interactions inside with YouFight: the virtual platform hosting the craziest fights! FEATURES Discover a stylized and colorful cartoon universe based on the top gaming YouTubers! Play as Poodiepie (Pewdiepie) and ToastyKen (Cinnamontoastken) and fight with fast and easy chainable combos! Experiment various mini-games & humorous interactions inside with YouFight, a fancy parody of YouTube hosting the craziest fights!
